Important information

Ingredients:

Ingredients: water, 19% cheddar cheese, sweet whey, soya oil, modified starch, salt, acidifier lactic acid, aroma, melting salt sodium phosphates, thickening agent xanthan gum, preservative sorbic acid, dye paprika extract.

Directions:

For easy removal, the bottle at approx. 300 watts for 20 seconds with the lid open in the microwave. Repeat once if necessary.

Legal Disclaimer

Actual product packaging and materials may contain more and different information than what is shown on our app or website. We recommend that you do not rely solely on the information presented here and that you always read labels, warnings, and directions before using or consuming a product.

Product description

Product Description

Old Fashioned Squeeze Cheese is the "must" for the perfect TV evening. Easy to use for garnishing, not just for nachos, there are no limits to your imagination. Be it hot dogs, hamburgers, sandwiches, chips or crackers, it just fits anywhere. Convenient to prepare in the microwave and enjoy the warm cheese as you normally can only in the cinema or at the Mexican.

Ingredients

Ingredients: water, 19% cheddar cheese, sweet whey, soya oil, modified starch, salt, acidifier lactic acid, aroma, melting salt sodium phosphates, thickening agent xanthan gum, preservative sorbic acid, dye paprika extract.

Directions

For easy removal, the bottle at approx. 300 watts for 20 seconds with the lid open in the microwave. Repeat once if necessary.
